# Directions to L100 Deikhan Fight Trainer (Knight Templar, mob 269)

say { "hello";
	bow %n;
	say Hello %n, what service can I render?;
	}
        
say { "next trainer";
	tell %n Finding your next trainer is part of your training.;
	tell %n However, I can give you a hint.;
 	tell %n Seek the knight defending the home of his deity.;
	tell %n But you must have water breath to get to him.;
	tell %n Pelicans and seagulls fly, from there head east;
	tell %n into the cold waters where fish-bone swords lie.; 
	}

